15% respectively.</p><p>Rival Richemont, which is more focused on high-end timepieces, last month reported quarterly sales growth of 9% despite lower sales in China. The world's biggest luxury group LVMH said last week that sales of its watches and jewellery rose 4% last year.</p>","headline":"Swatch sees 20% profit jump in 2013 and predicts strong year ahead","trailText":"Swiss watch firm reports good sales as net profit rose to Sfr1.9bn, beating estimates for Sfr1.6bn","newspaperPageNumber":"26","shouldHideAdverts":"false","publication":"The Guardian","showInRelatedContent":"true","shortUrl":"http://gu.com/p/3mfz3","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/5/1391627138748/SWATCH-006.jpg","secureThumbnail":"https://static-secure.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/2/5/1391627138748/SWATCH-006.jpg","wordcount":"286","commentable":"false","internalContentCode":"429004859","allowUgc":"false","internalOctopusCode":"8650492","isPremoderated":"false","byline":"Reuters","newspaperEditionDate":"2014-02-06T00:00:00Z","internalPageCode":"2038935","productionOffice":"UK","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-02-08T19:12:29Z"},"rights":{"syndicatable":false,"subscriptionDatabases":false},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/business/2014/feb/05/swatch-profit-sales-jump-forecast","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/business/2014/feb/05/swatch-profit-sales-jump-forecast","tags":[{"id":"business/retail","webTitle":"Retail industry","type":"keyword","sectionId":"business","sectionName":"Business","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/business/retail","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/business/retail","references":[]},{"id":"world/switzerland","webTitle":"Switzerland","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/switzerland","apiUrl":"http://internal.content.guardianapis.com/world/switzerland","references":[]},{"id":"business/bus